      "writtenOn": "2020-09-08T13:40:01Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Added asserts. I like John\u0027s sentinel pattern, but unfortunately it leads to a lot of \"unhandled enumeration value in switch\" issues due to unhandled sentinels, so we either need to specifically add cases for the sentinels (ugly) or use a default (unsafe). Given how often we switch on these enums, and how rarely I expect we\u0027ll add new enum values, I personally feel like it\u0027s better to keep the switches clean.",
      "parentUuid": "3112e15b_71b5c56b",
